### Delete todo item - REPLACE WITH ACTUAL ITEM ID
DELETE http://localhost:3001/api/items/REPLACE_WITH_ITEM_ID

### Delete non-existent item (404 error)
DELETE http://localhost:3001/api/items/citemnonexistent1234567890123

### Delete item with invalid ID format (400 error)
DELETE http://localhost:3001/api/items/invalid-id-format